%% Activity: OverviewPage 進入 → 觸發建立 Issue Modal 的 UX 路徑
%% 對應 User Stories: US-V-001 / US-V-007
%% 對應 AC: AC-Group 1 Rule「RoadmapPage 應在 canSubmitIssue=true 時顯示建立 issue 按鈕」、AC-Group 4（OverviewPage 分區）、AC-Group 8（向後相容：缺 canSubmitIssue 視為 false）
%% 對應 ADR: ADR-004（canSubmitIssue 計算 + 兩區塊分區）

flowchart TD
    Visitor[[訪客]]
    Summary[(public/data/summary.json)]
    Overview[(OverviewPage)]
    Roadmap[(RoadmapPage)]

    Visitor -->|1. 開啟儀表板根路徑 #/| Overview
    Overview --> LoadSummary[loadSummary 讀取 summary.json]
    LoadSummary --> Summary
    Summary --> Partition[依 canSubmitIssue 分流 repos]

    Partition --> SubmittableGroup[submittableRepos = repos.filter canSubmitIssue === true]
    Partition --> BrowseOnlyGroup[browseOnlyRepos = repos.filter canSubmitIssue !== true 含缺欄位 向後相容]

    SubmittableGroup --> RenderSubmittable[渲染「接受訪客提交」區塊 RepoCard grid 依原排序 可在此建立 issue badge]
    BrowseOnlyGroup --> RenderBrowseOnly[渲染「僅供瀏覽」折疊區塊 預設 collapsed 標題含數量]

    RenderSubmittable --> UserChoice[[訪客選擇 repo 進入點]]
    RenderBrowseOnly --> UserChoice

    UserChoice --> WhichCard{點擊哪一區?}

    WhichCard -- 接受訪客提交區 --> ClickSubmittable[點擊 RepoCard]
    ClickSubmittable --> NavigateRoadmap[navigate #/repo/:name]
    NavigateRoadmap --> Roadmap

    WhichCard -- 僅供瀏覽區 --> ClickBrowseOnly[點擊列表項目]
    ClickBrowseOnly --> ExternalGitHub[開新分頁外連到 github.com/zenbuapps/:name 不進入 SPA RoadmapPage]

    Roadmap --> LoadDetail[loadRepoDetail :name 讀取 repos/:name.json]
    LoadDetail --> GetCanSubmit[從 AppShell Outlet context 的 summary 取得該 repo 的 canSubmitIssue]
    GetCanSubmit --> HeaderCheck{canSubmitIssue === true?}

    HeaderCheck -- 否 --> HidePageBtn[PageHeader 不顯示建立 Issue 按鈕 僅顯示開啟 GitHub Repo 按鈕]
    HidePageBtn --> BrowseMilestones[[訪客瀏覽 milestones 與 issues 僅讀取模式]]

    HeaderCheck -- 是 --> ShowPageBtn[PageHeader 顯示建立 Issue 按鈕 btn-primary Plus 圖示 md 斷點響應式堆疊]
    ShowPageBtn --> UserClickCreate[[訪客點擊建立 Issue 按鈕]]
    UserClickCreate --> OpenIssueModal[setOpenIssueModal true 開啟 VisitorIssueModal]
    OpenIssueModal --> HandoffToSubmit[交棒至 submit-issue.mmd 流程]
